These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
City: colone, hamburg, new-york, liverpool
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, grey, chestnut, pink
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, salsa, r&b, trance
1. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
3. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
4. the person traveling to colone is the person who likes apricot##1
5. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
6. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
7. the person who likes grey is on the left of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| City    | hamburg  | liverpool | new-york    | colone       |
| Color         | grey | pink    | chestnut      | apricot |
| Music-Genre   | jazz   | r&b | salsa | trance        |

