.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
House: ranch-style, modern, cape-cod, art-deco
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, almond-milk, soy-milk, tea
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, daffodil, lily, zinnia
1. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
2. the art-deco house is on the right of the person who growslily##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
4. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
5. the person who growstulip is the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person who growszinnia is the modern house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| House        | cape-cod   | modern | ranch-style     | art-deco      |
| Beverage         | almond-milk | soy-milk | tea | mirinda |
| Flower   | daffodil    | zinnia   | lily     | tulip      |

