.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, water, fanta
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, cain, aristoff, havana
4 different games are played: go, backgammon, canasta, chess
1. the cain-smoker is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person drinking water##1
3. the havana-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking fanta is the aristoff-smoker##1
5. the person playing chess is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
6. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
7. the person drinking cola is the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage         | cola | hot-chocolate | water | fanta |
| Cigar   | havana       | cain    | alhambra | aristoff     |
| Game   | go | canasta    | chess | backgammon    |

