.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, drama, romance, musical
There 4 different types of food: radish, banana, tomato, onion
House: victorian, cottage, colonial, futuristic
1. the person watching romance movies is the futuristic house##1
2. the person eating banana is on the far left##1
3. the colonial house is on the right of the futuristic house##1
4. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
5. the person eating tomato is on the far right##1
6. the person eating radish is the person watching romance movies##1
7. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
8. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre         | thriller | musical | romance | drama |
| Food       | banana     | onion      | radish     | tomato      |
| House   | cottage | victorian         | futuristic      | colonial        |

