.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, backgammon, canasta, domino
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, scientist, social-worker, electrician
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, dutch, pakistani, egyptian
1. the scientist is on the far right##1
2. the person playing canasta is on the far left##1
3. the dutch is on the right of the chef##1
4. the russian is the social-worker##1
5. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the dutch##1
6. the person playing scrabble is the scientist##1
7. the person playing domino is the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Game         | canasta   | domino | backgammon  | scrabble      |
| Job   | social-worker  | chef        | electrician  | scientist       |
| Nationality         | russian | pakistani    | dutch | egyptian |

