.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, rose, begonia, balloon-flower
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, october, august, march
City: rome, london, nizza, liverpool
1. the person who growspoppy is the person traveling to london##1
2. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left##1
5. the person who growsrose is on the far left##1
6. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who growsbegonia##1
7. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
8. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Flower           | rose | begonia | balloon-flower | poppy |
| Birthday   | march   | august  | october | july   |
| City   | liverpool   | rome     | nizza | london       |

