.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, helicopter, taxi, van
House: cottage, colonial, futuristic, ranch-style
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, fonseca, ritmeester, vegafina
1. the futuristic house is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the far right##1
3. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
4. the fonseca-smoker is the person driving the taxi##1
5. the colonial house is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
6. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
7. the cottage house is on the right of the colonial house##1
8. the colonial house is the baccarat-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Transport          | scooter  | van | taxi   | helicopter     |
| House         | ranch-style | colonial   | cottage  | futuristic |
| Cigar   | ritmeester         | baccarat  | fonseca | vegafina  |

