.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, brown, lilac, chestnut
House: victorian, wooden, cottage, art-deco
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, indie, classical, rock
1. the person who likes brown is the fan of classical##1
2. the fan of rock is on the right of the art-deco house##1
3. the wooden house is on the far right##1
4. the cottage house is on the left of the fan of classical##1
5. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the victorian house##1
6. the fan of rock is the person who likes lilac##1
7. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of rock##1
8. the person who likes brown is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Color      | chestnut | lilac     | orange | brown |
| House   | art-deco  | victorian | cottage       | wooden    |
| Music-Genre   | indie   | rock | blues    | classical |

