.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, dancing, hiking, cooking
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, bus, skateboard, tram
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, doctor, electrician, freelancer
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the freelancer is on the right of the electrician##1
3. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the electrician is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
6. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
7. the doctor is on the left of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Hobby          | hiking        | cooking   | dancing  | magic-tricks   |
| Transport   | ship         | tram     | bus    | skateboard       |
| Job         | doctor | scientist | electrician | freelancer |

