4. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
5. the person traveling to nizza is on the far right##1
6. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
7. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
