.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, july, september, april
There 4 different types of food: spinach, cabbage, artichoke, peach
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, mauve, turquise, black
1. the person who likes lavender is on the far left##1
2. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person eating peach##1
4. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating peach##1
5. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
6. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
7. the person eating spinach is the person who likes turquise##1
8. the person eating artichoke is the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Birthday         | june  | april | july  | september |
| Food       | artichoke | cabbage        | peach | spinach       |
| Color   | lavender   | mauve          | black          | turquise       |

