.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-12::.
City: nizza, miami, liverpool, london
4 different pets are kept: lizard, mouse, cat, frog
House: modern, wooden, cottage, futuristic
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the frog is the person traveling to miami##1
3. the futuristic house is on the left of the modern house##1
4. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
6. the person traveling to nizza is the cottage house##1
7. the futuristic house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| City         | london   | liverpool   | nizza | miami |
| Pet   | cat | lizard | mouse   | frog |
| House   | futuristic     | modern  | cottage  | wooden  |

