.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-13::.
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, onion, lemon, cherry
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, green, brown, white
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, action, thriller, zombie
1. the person eating onion is on the left of the person who likes white##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is the person who likes white##1
3. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
5. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person who likes green##1
6. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
7. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Food         | cherry | onion    | nectarine        | lemon |
| Color   | green     | brown     | white        | grey   |
| Movie-Genre         | action   | comedy | thriller | zombie  |

