There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, turquise, black, brown
1. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing whist##1
2. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
3. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
4. the person playing backgammon is the person who likes black##1
5. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
6. the person who growsdahlia is the person playing scrabble##1
7. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person who growsiris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Game          | whist     | domino   | scrabble | backgammon |
| Flower   | daisy | tulip | dahlia | iris   |
| Color           | brown    | turquise     | chestnut      | black     |

