.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-17::.
There 4 different types of food: pear, cherry, apple, kale
4 different games are played: whist, chess, snooker, mah-jongg
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, oliveros, pall-mall, fonseca
1. the person playing chess is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
2. the person eating cherry is the person playing chess##1
3. the person playing whist is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
4. the person playing snooker is the oliveros-smoker##1
5. the person eating apple is on the far left##1
6. the person eating kale is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
7. the pall-mall-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Food           | apple  | pear | cherry  | kale |
| Game   | snooker    | whist       | chess | mah-jongg      |
| Cigar   | oliveros | havana  | fonseca    | pall-mall    |

