.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, almond-milk, 7up, coffee
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, jet-ski, subway, helicopter
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, singing, sudoku, woodworking
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the airplane is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
6. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Beverage           | almond-milk  | 7up  | mirinda | coffee |
| Transport   | helicopter   | airplane | jet-ski   | subway      |
| Hobby         | collecting | sudoku    | singing   | woodworking         |

 